Citizens in countries from Germany to France are beginning to protest as their energy bills continue to skyrocket. From Italy lighting candles due to the intense increase on their energy bills, to the UK now hosting game shows where getting your “energy bill” paid is now a huge prize, we can look to Europe’s green energy policies and dependency on Russian oil, as an example as to what could come to America if we continue to rely on foreign oil while pushing ineffective green energy policies. Lewis Brackpool, Rebel news reporter and UK citizen joins me to discuss.&#13;
